graph TD
    UI[React Webclient]
    CoreServer[Core Server Node.js]
    TrackServer[Tracking Service]
    TrackList[(Redis Tracking List)]
    Postgres[(PostgreSQL Users/Watchlists)]
    RMQ{{RabbitMQ}}
    
    subgraph Watchlist Registration
        UI -->|1. HTTP POST Add 'NVDA' to Watchlist| CoreServer
        CoreServer -->|2. Save User Preference| Postgres
        CoreServer -->|3. HTTP Add 'NVDA' to Daily Tracker| TrackServer
        TrackServer -->|4. Save to Tracking List| TrackList
    end
    
    subgraph Real-Time Alert Flow
        RMQ -->|5. Deliver Analyzed Article for NVDA| CoreServer
        CoreServer -->|6. Check if Score Shifted Drastically| CoreServer
        CoreServer -->|7. Cross-Reference Affected Users| Postgres
        CoreServer -.->|8. SSE Push Notification 'NVDA Alert!'| UI
    end